description:
"SadoMamiHolic" by beatMARIO(COOL&CREATE), "DesireDrive" by Kisida Kyodan, etc, we have prepared popular songs that are as good as the other arrangement packs!

This pack contains the following: 

■6 Songs
・Monochrome in the Night / ShibayanRecords
・Initial Initial Echo Ego / Diao ye zong
・Another Lovely Day for this Lively Graveyard / Akatsuki Records
・DesireDrive / Kisida Kyodan & The Akebosi Rockets
・Can't look away / FELT
・SadoMamiHolic / beatMARIO(COOL&CREATE)

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv.5 The Worrisome Mother of Gensokyo (Monochrome in the Night)
・Lv.6 In Your Own Words (Initial Initial Echo Ego)
・Lv.7 Look at This Mess (Another Lovely Day for this Lively Graveyard)
・Lv.8 The Truth (DesireDrive)
・Lv.9 Not So Easy! (Can't look away)
・Lv.10 Buddha in a Shinto Shrine (SadoMamiHolic)

 * Internet connection required for purchase.
 * Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou Shinreibyo Arrangements Pack
